title: Haydn - London Symphonies - Davis, Royal Concertgebouw
description:
Haydn: The London Symphonies, (93, 94, 96, 97, 99 - 104).

Sir Colin Davis recorded the twelve London Symphonies of Haydn with the Royal Concertgebouw Orchestra in the late 70s and early 80s. In 1994, Philips released the remastered recordings in their "Dou" series--twelve symphonies on 4 CDs.

NB: Because I have irrevocably lost one of the discs in this collection, the two symphonies 95 and 98 are missing from this torrent. Sorry.

Please enjoy, nevertheless.
